# How to generate the binary package from the sources
```sh
PKG_NAME=odbc-fdw
PKG_VERSION=0.0.1

mkdir /tmp/${PKG_NAME}
cd /tmp/${PKG_NAME}

# Get the source tarball from a tag
wget -O ${PKG_NAME}_${PKG_VERSION}.orig.tar.gz https://github.com/CartoDB/odbc_fdw/archive/${PKG_VERSION}.tar.gz

tar -xzf ${PKG_NAME}_${PKG_VERSION}.orig.tar.gz
cd ${PKG_NAME}_${PKG_VERSION}
debuild -us -uc
```
